trans-unit.source: Provides the base functionality for creating collections.

The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BaseCollection> class and its members are not intended for use as a stand-alone component, but as the class from which other collection classes derive standard functionality.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Data.InternalDataCollectionBase"></xref> class.

The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BaseCollection> class and its members are not intended for use as a stand-alone component, but as the class from which other collection classes derive standard functionality.

Copies all the elements of the current <xref href="System.Data.InternalDataCollectionBase"></xref> to a one-dimensional <xref:System.Array>, starting at the specified <xref href="System.Data.InternalDataCollectionBase"></xref> index.
This method can be overridden by a derived class.

The destination <xref:System.Array> index to start copying into.
